===========
Unofficial Python Bandcamp API Wrapper
===========

Disclaimer
==========
No warranty, express or implied. This module is not officaly endorsed by Bandcamp.

What do we have here?
=====================
A lightweight, easy to use wrapper around the official Bandcamp API.

Example usage
-------------

    #!/usr/bin/env python

    import bandcamp
    
    bandcamp.API_KEY = 'your-secret-api-key'
    url_obj = bandcamp.Url('http://lapfox.bandcamp.com/')
    band_obj = bandcamp.Band(url_obj.band_id)
    
    albums, tracks = band_obj.discography()
